{
  "chapter": 21,
  "chapter_summary": "本章以血奴闯入大堂为开端，她先看望重伤的甘老头，随即扼住昏迷的李大娘咽喉，却终因母女亲情未下杀手，改为掌掴将其唤醒。二人展开激烈对话：李大娘质问血奴为何不趁机杀她，血奴冷笑回应；李大娘追问韦七娘下落，得知血奴被韦七娘藏于后花园小楼夹壁并封住穴道。对话揭示武三爷对庄院的威胁，以及血奴虽名为血奴却非十三血奴之一的矛盾身份。李大娘暗示手中掌握着血鹦鹉和一张重要的纸，以此要挟血奴等人完成某项任务。章节末尾描写李大娘与血奴站在一起时的美貌对比，暗示李大娘可能驻颜有术，实际年纪与外貌不符。全章通过母女对峙，逐步揭露血鹦鹉秘密的一角，营造出紧张悬疑的氛围。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "除了掌掴，你难道没有其他的办法将我弄醒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你掴的倒也不轻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我就觉得实在太轻了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "看你的样子，好像要杀了我才甘心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "方才那么好的机会，你怎么不下手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我怎敢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你的确不敢。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "韦七娘呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "她不是跟你在一起？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "将你藏起来总该是她了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "是她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "她将你藏在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "后花园那座小楼的夹壁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "是什么时候的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "大概是午后三刻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你居然老老实实的在那里待了半天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "她封住了我的穴道，我就想不待在那里也不成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "她突然出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "到现在才冲开穴道出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我也想早一点出来瞧瞧热闹，只可惜我的内力实在太不济。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "这未尝不是一件好事，否则你现在可能已成刀下之鬼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "这一点我倒很放心，武三爷如果真的要毁我，我已不知死了多少次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "他一直不打你的主意，只不过时机尚未成熟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "时机成熟，他就再不会留情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "他虽然未必会杀你，落在他的手中，你也绝不会好受。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你其实不该叫做血奴的，你也根本就不是个血奴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "这又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "血奴是血鹦鹉的奴才，他既然一心要追查血鹦鹉的秘密，找不到血鹦鹉，又怎会不追问你这个血奴？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "好像他这种人，要追问他人，一定有很多办法，一定会不择手段。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你不择手段，还是他不择手段？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "比较起来，我的不择手段好得多了，最低限度我很少使用武力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你根本不敢使用武力。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "所以你应该感激韦七娘才是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "只不知她现在死了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你很想她死？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "不想，现在正是我需要用人的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你肯定她会听你的吩咐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "但无论如何，她只要还有一口气，都不会让你被人伤害，你留在我身旁，她就算不想保护我也不成，何况还有另一个她必须保护我的理由。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我似乎没有留在你身旁的必要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "我看就有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "因为我随时都已准备离开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "一个人离开？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "不是一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你现在是不是还肯留在我身旁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你不怕我们将人半途抢走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你可曾见我做过没有把握的事情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你真的这样贪心，到现在仍不满足？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你们已经很接近目的了，为什么不努力完成它？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    }
